			<p style="text-align:justify">
				The Eclipse Persistence Services Project (EclipseLink)
				delivers a comprehensive open-source Java persistence
				solution.
				EclipseLink focuses on standards with advanced
				features, performance
				and scalability for enterprise
				software developers across data
				sources, formats, and
				containers.
